name: Kizkumu
description: I took this picture in Kizkumu and edited digitally back in 2018. Kizkumu is an area of 600 meters shallow water that divides this bay of Turkey. According to the legend, a girl who wants to reach her lover fills her skirt with sand and start moving ahead in the sea by filling the sea with her sand. But she was drowned when she ran out of sand. Just at the beginning point of the shallow water area, there is a sculpture of this girl.
